===========
Power Droid
===========

Google laboratory, data acquisition, and instrument control framework.

Provides at least the following:

A basic lab automation framework that utilizes GPIB/IEEE-488/SCPI
instruments. Includes modules for measuring, reporting, and graphing. 

Includes command line tools for taking measurements and reporting results.

Controller interfaces for project Android and other devices.

Test harness and test runner framework.

Persistent data storage.

A web browser application for reporting and interactive testing.


